Package org.gephi.project.spi

SPI for workspace capabilities and project managment UI.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProjectPropertiesUI
    Interface for setting project meta-data dialog.
    WorkspaceBytesPersistenceProvider
    This class is similar to WorkspacePersistenceProvider except that it allows bytes serialization instead of XML.
    WorkspaceDuplicateProvider
    Interface to implement workspace duplicate providers.
    WorkspacePersistenceProvider
    Interface modules implement to notify the system they can read/write part of the .gephi project file to serialize states and data.

Package org.gephi.project.spi Description

SPI for workspace capabilities and project managment UI.

Modules can implement workspace capabilites to interact with workspace life cycle.
